&lt;li&gt;Over $300 million raised in funding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Over 2,800 Tideans globally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognised with Great Place to Work certification three years in a row, and among India’s Top 50 Best Workplaces in Banking, Financial Services, and Insurance in 2026&lt;/li&gt;
