&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Follow-Up:&lt;/strong&gt; Aggressively follow up on event-generated leads using CRM tools to maximize final conversion rates and drive paid plan adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
